                        i.material-icons.activator info

                .card-reveal
                    span.card-title
                        h4 Amazon.com
                        i.material-icons.right close
                    p Earth's biggest online selection of books, magazines, music, DVDs, videos, electronics, computers, software, apparel &amp; accessories, shoes, jewelry ...
